<div class="body">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p class="topnotice">
Please visit the <a href="http://doc.ntp.org/">NTP Documentation Archive</a> to search the documentation for Stable Releases of The NTP Reference Implementation.
</p>
</div>
<p>
This search will allow you to search the contents of all the publicly
available WWW documents for the NTP Project at: 
</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/">ntp.org</a> - includes the NTP FAQ</li>
<li>the <a href="http://www.eecis.udel.edu/~mills/ntp.html">Network Time Synchronization Project</a> page</li>
<li>the <a href="http://www.eecis.udel.edu/~mills/ntp">Information on Time and Frequency Services</a> page - includes the current NTP-Dev Documentation</li>
</ul>
<br />
